{"tid":2398483,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"歐議員倡為港人設「救生艇」","createTime":"2021-02-07T10:37:49.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-07T10:41:05.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"e27488fe8729d7b5b839aa7bc6d44f0727385652","tid":2398483,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T10:37:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210207/XEONIZ5EPRFIRBTMR4Z72S44J4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210207%2FXEONIZ5EPRFIRBTMR4Z72S44J4%2F&d=NdDBecmRZzhky7sLgKmJOT11NNBcSSu27FcfjCvRQ4I%3D&h=ff1c8049\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210207%2FXEONIZ5EPRFIRBTMR4Z72S44J4%2F&h=956a34b1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210207/XEONIZ5EPRFIRBTMR4Z72S44J4/</a><br />\n<br />\n歐議員倡為港人設「救生艇」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/zuBt22b9EeTmuFQLCR-BsjsukYk=/1000x563/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/WLHRQXAFN5CNPMFEUXYXXRXGMY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FzuBt22b9EeTmuFQLCR-BsjsukYk%3D%2F1000x563%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FWLHRQXAFN5CNPMFEUXYXXRXGMY.jpg&h=cbf103b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】香港政治局勢持續受到國際關注，斯<br />\n洛伐克籍歐洲議會議員萊克斯曼（Miriam Lexmann，圖）撰文，。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n確保有代表旁聽泛民聆訊<br />\n<br />\n萊克斯曼前天在比利時《新歐洲報》刊出的文章，題為〈歐洲必須支持香港〉，當中指她前年曾以國際代表團身份觀察香港區議會選舉，民主派當時大勝反映香港人「渴望實踐其權利和自由，及維持高度自治」，但選舉結果令港府及北京大為震驚，繼而大舉反擊港人。她把香港現況及未來比喻為歐盟及民主世界的實驗試紙，又指「我們已發出夠多的聲明，但還未足夠引起關注」。<br />\n<br />\n她認為歐盟可作出的實際行動包括停止與香港的引渡協議，並推出給港人的「救生艇計劃」；歐盟訂立清楚的政策支持香港公民社會，例如確保定期旁聽民主派人士及政治人物的審訊，以及讓領事接觸雙重國籍的被拘留人士；動用歐盟版《馬格尼茨基制裁法》制裁林鄭月娥及其他要為侵犯人權的中港官員；最後是必須讓中共明白，歐洲議會在審議《中歐全面投資協定》時，會考慮人權事宜。"},{"pid":"ce0929e823528049f4ee8392f390a066f6e48067","tid":2398483,"uid":57677,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T10:41:05.000Z","msg":"「左膠國唔去都罷」"}]}